  • Constructor Details

    • PromotionalSet

      public PromotionalSet​(String name, MainCourse main, Sides side, Drinks drink)
      Create a new promotional object with its set name and combination of main,sides,drink with a overall discounted price.
      Parameters:
      name - this promotional set name.
      main - this main course dish object that is included in this set.
      side - this side dish object that is included in this set.
      drink - this drink object that is included in this set.

      public void setPrice()
      Update the price of this promotional set. Cost of promotional set = floor((price of main + price of side + price of drink)*0.9)
